# Card render (layout builder)

Read `.cursor/AGENTS.md` and `skills/generate-card-json/SKILL.md` before generating or editing card JSON.

## Mode detection

- **Composed**: `children` has any top-level `card-header`, `card-content`, or `card-footer` → legacy flat props ignored.
- **Legacy**: no such slots → use `title`, `description`, `headerAction`, `footer`, `children` (body in CardContent).

## JSON rules

- Root type: `"card"`. Slot types: `card-header`, `card-title`, `card-description`, `card-action`, `card-content`, `card-footer`.
- `card-title` / `card-description`: required `text` string.
- `size`: `"default"` | `"sm"` only.
- Composed order: typically `card-header` → `card-content` → `card-footer`.
- Legacy: `children` = body inside CardContent; auto `pt-6` when no header.

## Pitfalls

- Mixing legacy `title` with composed `card-header` in same card — pick one mode.
- Using `label` on `card-title` — use `text`.
- Empty card with no header/content — add at least body `children` or `card-content`.
